G.L. c. 231, \u00a7 85.proposition: This action arises under the negligence law of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts, including but not limited to the principles established in **G.L. c. 231, § 85**, and relevant case law recognizing the duty of care owed by childcare providers to protect children from foreseeable harm.

G.L. c. 223, \u00a7 1.proposition: Venue is proper under **G.L. c. 223, § 1** as the events giving rise to this claim occurred at Defendant’s community center in Brockton, Massachusetts.
